tes\", \"pod_cpu_usage\", \"pod_fs_writes_bytes\"],\n  \"hypotheses\": [\n    {\n      \"component\": \"redis-cart-0\",\n      \"reason\": \"pod_processes 指标从正常值1.0变为0.0，变化率200%，表明Pod进程终止或重启\",\n      \"evidence\": \"pod_processes: 正常中位数1.0 -> 故障中位数0.0 (变化率200%)\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"productcatalogservice-1\",\n      \"reason\": \"pod_network_transmit_packets 和 pod_network_receive_packets 指标归零，网络流量中断\",\n      \"evidence\": \"pod_network_transmit_packets: 112.85 -> 0.0 (变化率200%), pod_network_receive_packets: 102.44 -> 0.0 (变化率200%)\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"frontend-0\",\n      \"reason\": \"pod_network_transmit_packets 和 pod_network_receive_packets 指标归零，网络通信中断\",\n      \"evidence\": \"pod_network_transmit_packets: 39.69 -> 0.0 (变化率200%), pod_network_receive_packets: 30.93 -> 0.0 (变化率200%)\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"frontend-2\",\n      \"reason\": \"pod_network_transmit_packets 和 pod_network_receive_packets 指标归零，网络通信中断\",\n      \"evidence\": \"pod_network_transmit_packets: 30.33 -> 0.0 (变化率200%), pod_network_receive_packets: 23.66 -> 0.0 (变化率200%)\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"frontend-1\",\n      \"reason\": \"pod_network_transmit_packets 和 pod_network_receive_packets 指标归零，网络通信中断\",\n      \"evidence\": \"pod_network_transmit_packets: 29.9 -> 0.0 (变化率200%), pod_network_receive_packets: 23.71 -> 0.0 (变化率200%)\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"adservice-0\",\n      \"reason\": \"pod_memory_working_set_bytes 指标从2874.46变为0.0，内存使用异常归零\",\n      \"evidence\": \"pod_memory_working_set_bytes: 2874.46 -> 0.0 (变化率200%)\"\n    }\n  ]\n}\n```\n\n## 分析总结\n\n**关键发现**：\n1. **最显著异常**：`redis-cart-0` Pod的`pod_processes`指标从1.0变为0.0，表明该Pod进程完全终止，这是最严重的故障信号。\n\n2. **网络通信中断**：多个关键服务的Pod网络指标（包括数据包收发）在故障期间归零，表明存在大规模网络通信中断：\n   - `productcatalogservice-1`（产品目录服务）\n   - `frontend-0`、`frontend-1`、`frontend-2`（前端服务）\n   - `checkoutservice-2`（结账服务）\n   - `currencyservice-1`（货币服务）\n\n3. **内存使用异常**：`adservice-0`的内存使用指标归零，可能与Pod